---

<BaseLayout
  title="구축사례 | (주)이즈소프트"
  description="제조, 식품, 자동차부품, 의료기기 등 다양한 분야에서 축적된 이즈소프트의 솔루션 도입 사례를 확인하세요."
  lang={lang}
  currentPath={currentPath}
>
  <Header slot="header" lang={lang} currentPath={currentPath} />

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero" aria-label="페이지 헤더">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-hero__breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">홈</a>
        <span>&gt;</span>
        <span>구축사례</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Reference</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__desc">이즈소프트의 솔루션을 통해 혁신을 달성한 대표 구축 사례입니다.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Portfolio Section (Refactored to 2-Column Row List for enhanced readability) -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="portfolio-title">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="sr-only" id="portfolio-title">구축사례 목록</h2>

      <!-- Modern vertical card rows (Feedback: Removed popup dialogs, improved readability) -->
      <div class="portfolio-list-wrapper">
        {projects.map((proj, i) => (
          <div class="portfolio-row-card fade-in" style={`animation-delay: ${i * 0.05}s`}>
            <!-- Strict container to hold partner logo without stretch -->
            <div class="portfolio-row-card__logo-wrapper">
              <img
                src={proj.logo}
                alt={`${proj.name} 로고`}
                class="portfolio-row-card__logo"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-row-card__content">
              <div class="portfolio-row-card__meta">
                <span class="badge">{proj.sector}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="portfolio-row-card__title">{proj.name}</h3>
              <p class="portfolio-row-card__desc">{proj.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" lang={lang} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* 2-Column Row List Styles for maximum readability */
  .portfolio-list-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .portfolio-row-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .portfolio-row-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-brand-orange);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Logo wrapper container */
  .portfolio-row-card__logo-wrapper {
    width: 160px;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  /* Force contain aspect ratio strictly to prevent stretching */
  .portfolio-row-card__logo {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 80px;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Content area */
  .portfolio-row-card__content {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .portfolio-row-card__meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .portfolio-row-card__id {
    font-family: var(--font-english);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .portfolio-row-card__title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .portfolio-row-card__desc {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Responsive breakpoints */
  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .portfolio-list-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 575px) {
    .portfolio-row-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .portfolio-row-card__logo-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      height: 120px;
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    }
  }
</style>
